'''遠東博物館'''（{{lang-nl|Brusselse Musea van het Verre Oosten}}, {{lang-fr|Musées d’Extrême-Orient de Bruxelles}}）是位於[[比利時|比利時]][[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]][[拉肯|拉肯]]地區的一座[[博物館|博物館]]，展示日本和中國的工藝品，也是比利時[[皇家艺术与历史博物馆|皇家艺术与历史博物馆]]的一部分。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.belgium-tourism.be/informations/tourist-attractions-laeken-museums-of-the-far-east-royal-museums-for-art-and-history-brussels/en/V/17567.html|title=Museums of the Far East - Royal Museums for Art and History, Brussels|accessdate=2016-03-01|author=|date=|publisher=Belgium Tourism|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121113947/http://belgium-tourism.be/informations/tourist-attractions-laeken-museums-of-the-far-east-royal-museums-for-art-and-history-brussels/en/V/17567.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.brusselsmuseums.be/en/museum/94-museums-of-the-far-east-royal-museums-of-art-and-history|title=Museums of the Far East (Royal Museums of Art and History)|accessdate=2016-03-01|author=|date=|publisher=Brussel's Museums|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304104138/http://www.brusselsmuseums.be/en/museum/94-museums-of-the-far-east-royal-museums-of-art-and-history|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.kmkg-mrah.be/history-0|title=History|accessdate=2016-03-01|author=|date=|publisher=[[皇家艺术与历史博物馆|KMKG]]|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127034955/http://www.kmkg-mrah.be/history-0|dead-url=no}}</ref>博物館創建於1904年，1905年起正式对外开放，擁有法國人建築師設計的日式五重塔和中國式寺廟。<ref name=":0" />博物馆自2013年起因建筑安全原因需要闭馆整修，停止开放。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kmkg-mrah.be/node/2743|title=Closure of the Museums of the Far East|accessdate=2016-03-01|author=|date=2013-10-25|publisher=|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215122204/http://www.kmkg-mrah.be/node/2743|dead-url=no}}</ref>

